0  1        2  3  3  2     1  0  INCLUDE-WHITESPACE=non-nil

The case where TAG is nil:
___<TAG ...>___
   0        0     INCLUDE-WHITESPACE=nil
0  1        1  0  INCLUDE-WHITESPACE=non-nil"
  (let ((init (point))
	(num 1)
	(md (match-data))
